# SSH host profiles for WebTerm/3270
# Format: id, name, host/IP, port, user
# Password is prompted at connect time — never stored here.
#
# Examples:
# mock-zvm, Mock z/VM SSH, mock-zvm, 22, ibmuser
# prod-uss, z/OS USS Production, 10.0.0.5, 22, sshuser
# linux-gw, Linux Gateway, 192.168.1.10, 22, admin
